# Interactive Tutorial Builder - Detailed Requirements

## Project Overview

Build an Agentic AI Workflow that automatically generates interactive tutorials for every session in a course.

The generated output should not be a static reading material or cheat sheet. Instead, it should be a guided learning experience that progressively reveals content, validates learner understanding through mandatory MCQs, and concludes with a session-level assessment.

The final output should be generated as HTML code that can be directly rendered inside the learning platform as a tutorial.

---

# Business Problem

Currently, learners consume content through reading materials, PPTs, and recorded sessions.

These resources are passive and do not actively verify whether the learner understands the concepts while learning.

Creating interactive tutorials manually is time-consuming and difficult to scale across thousands of sessions.

We need an automated system that converts session content into structured, interactive, assessment-driven tutorials.

